    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> ginger</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds, then cut the <strong>remaining red</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
