    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Once the chicken has browned, reduce the heat to medium-high and add a splash of<strong> water </strong>and cook, covered, for 10 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
