    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spring greens</strong>, then rip the leaves off, discard the tough stalks, and layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p>",
