      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pulled</strong> <strong>hoisin free range chicken thigh</strong> over the<strong> sesame noodles</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong>,<strong> chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
